OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,FA 28-year-old man has been arrested in
OL,8,FSouth Yorkshire on suspicion of the
OL,9,Fmurder of former MP and MEP Ann
OL,10,FWiddecombe, police said.
OL,12,FThe former Conservative minister, and
OL,13,Flater Reform UK spokesperson, was
OL,14,Ffound dead at her home in Haytor on
OL,15,FDartmoor at about 11.40am on Thursday
OL,16,Fafter sustaining serious injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
