PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783887686
OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,FA statement from Devon and Cornwall
OL,8,FPolice, late on Saturday, said: "We
OL,9,Fcan confirm that a 28-year-old man was
OL,10,Farrested at an address in the South
OL,11,FYorkshire area this evening (July 11)
OL,12,Fon suspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,13,FWiddecombe.
OL,15,F"The suspect, who is a white British
OL,16,Fnational, is now in police custody.
OL,18,F"Miss Widdecombe's family have been
OL,19,Finformed of this development.
OL,26,@pD@aOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
