CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783887686
OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,F"We were supported by Counter
OL,8,FTerrorism Policing North East and
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire Police who carried out
OL,10,Fthe arrest on behalf of Devon &
OL,11,FCornwall Police.
OL,13,F"At this time, there is still no
OL,14,Finformation to suggest that this is a
OL,15,Fterrorism-related incident and as a
OL,16,Fforce we retain primacy of the
OL,17,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@OO]
