CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783887686
OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police said earlier
OL,8,Fon Saturday it is believed Miss
OL,9,FWiddecombe was attacked on Wednesday
OL,10,Fat about 12.30pm.
OL,12,FMiss Widdecombe, who was 78, was first
OL,13,Felected a Conservative MP in Kent in
OL,14,F1987, went on to serve as an MEP for
OL,15,Fthe Brexit Party and then a
OL,16,Fspokeswoman for Reform UK.
OL,18,FShe also found fame outside politics
OL,19,Fafter starring in Strictly Come
OL,20,FDancing and Celebrity Big Brother.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783887686
OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,FMiss Widdecombe's personal driver of
OL,8,F10 years, Peter Horrell, lay flowers
OL,9,Fin front of her home on Saturday.
OL,11,FSpeaking to reporters, Mr Horrell said
OL,12,Fthe politician "never mentioned any
OL,13,Ffear" for her safety and loved living
OL,14,Fin Haytor.
OL,16,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage also
OL,17,Fvisited the village to pay tribute to
OL,18,FMiss Widdecombe on Saturday.
OL,26,@tD@POUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
