PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783887686
OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,FHis party's MPs have been given 24-
OL,8,Fhour security following Ms
OL,9,FWiddecombe's death, paid for by
OL,10,FReform, for fear of similar attacks.
OL,12,FITV News has published a series of
OL,13,FWhatsApp images which appear to show
OL,14,Fthat Miss Widdecombe stopped
OL,15,Fresponding to messages from a TV
OL,16,Fproducer after the approximate time
OL,17,Fpolice believe the attack took place
OL,18,Fon Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783887686
OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,FWhatsApp messages published by the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster show a conversation
OL,9,Fbetween Miss Widdecombe and a producer
OL,10,Ffrom Channel 5's Matt Allwright show,
OL,11,Fahead of her scheduled appearance on
OL,12,Fthe programme on Wednesday.
OL,14,FShe last sent a message at 12.19pm
OL,15,Fthat day acknowledging she had
OL,16,Freceived a Zoom link to appear on the
OL,17,Fprogramme, which read "Received! Panic
OL,18,FOver!"
OL,26,@yD@WOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783887686
OL,3,CPolice arrest 28-year-old man on
OL,4,Csuspicion of the murder of Ann
OL,5,CWiddecombe
OL,7,FBut Miss Widdecombe did not respond to
OL,8,Fa message asking her to join the Zoom
OL,9,Fcall at 12.48pm, and did not answer
OL,10,Ffurther calls or other messages
OL,11,Fattempting to contact her.
OL,13,FMr Allwright then confirmed at 1.27pm
OL,14,Flive on air she was booked to appear
OL,15,Fon the show, but had not turned up.
OL,17,FThe production team then followed up
OL,18,Fwith Miss Widdecombe's agent on
OL,19,FWednesday evening and Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
